          <p>MR. SPEAKER : The honourable Minister of Labour and Advanced Education.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#dec41d7a-1f3f-40db-bdc4-d55134cb9a68">
          <from>HON. MARILYN MORE</from>
          <p>HON. MARILYN MORE : Mr. Speaker, I beg leave to table the submissions to the first contract discussion paper posted recently on the Department of Labour and Advanced Education Web site. As well, I will table the mandate and membership of the Labour Management Review Committee and the Labour Board. Thank you.</p>
        </speech>
